{
  "title": "The Future of AI: Opportunities and Challenges",
  "article_text": "Artificial Intelligence (AI) is reshaping industries at an unprecedented pace. From healthcare to finance, machine‑learning models are delivering insights that were once impossible to obtain.\n\nHowever, this rapid adoption brings ethical dilemmas. Issues such as data privacy, algorithmic bias, and job displacement require proactive governance and transparent practices."
}
